  "body": "Logs info depict the opening of an MDBX database even if `--database=\"lmdb\"` has been set.\r\n\r\n```\r\n.\\build\\bin\\tg.exe --datadir E:\\tg --fakepow --database=\"lmdb\" --lmdb.mapSize=\"1100GB\"\r\n\r\nINFO [05-24|10:46:03.738] Build info                               git_branch=windows-build git_commit=c190a27fd20dae955fc5c3f4ff5b95f3190ce08a\r\nINFO [05-24|10:46:03.773] Starting Turbo-Geth on Ethereum mainnet...\r\nINFO [05-24|10:46:03.774] Maximum peer count                       ETH=50 total=50\r\nINFO [05-24|10:46:03.777] Set global gas cap                       cap=25000000\r\nINFO [05-24|10:46:03.817] Opening Database (LMDB)                  mapSize=\"1.1 TB\"\r\nINFO [05-24|10:46:03.920] database closed (MDBX)                   mdbx=inMem\r\n```\r\n\r\n",
